## 10. 执行命令参考

```bash
# L1a/b/c — 端侧全量（每次 PR，阻塞）
cd quwoquan_app && flutter test

# L1a 仅 contract（分类运行）
cd quwoquan_app && flutter test test/features/content/

# L1b 仅 widget
cd quwoquan_app && flutter test test/features/content/widgets/

# L1c 仅 journey
cd quwoquan_app && flutter test test/features/content/journeys/

# L2 — 云侧 contract（每次 PR，阻塞）
cd quwoquan_service && go test ./services/content-service/... -v -count=1

# L2 仅 contract tag
cd quwoquan_service && make test-contract

# L3 — API Contract（staging，daily）
STAGING_BASE_URL=https://staging.api.quwoquan.com make test-api-contract

# L4 — Patrol（pre-release，真实设备）
cd quwoquan_app && flutter test integration_test/ --dart-define=ENV=staging

# 门禁（本地开发）
make gate                # L1 + L2，阻塞合入
make gate-full           # L1 + L2 + L3，pre-release
```
